channel.title: My 718 Client Won't Load
channel.description:
I've been trying for the past 2 hours to try to get a client for my friends server up for him and when we go to run the client it won't load I tried all of the following No-ip, my real IP, and my localhost IP, and NONE of them worked, when I ran the client, it just stayed at "Checking for updates 0%"
I also get this in the command prompt when I run the client! "error_game_js5connect"
The Server is online and its loaded and the client will not work still!
Can somebody please help me out here! Please Much needed
